        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Bellicio <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Quar<lb break="no" n="2"/>tioni decurioni <lb n="3"/>Iuvavensium IIviro <lb n="4"/>iuris dicundi vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> LVIII <lb n="5"/>Sapliae Belatumarae <lb n="6"/>coniugi <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LXII Bellicius <lb n="7"/>Seccio et Bellicius Achilles <lb n="8"/>cum coniugibus ex testam<lb break="no" n="9"/>ento faciendum curaverunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>1944 durch Kriegseinwirkung zerstört. Nach Hameter gibt die Kopie in Burghausen nicht alle Buchstabenformen korrekt wieder. (B): Hameter: Z. 4: dicundo.</p>
            </div>
